<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=New_Imperialism&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.yale.edu/iss/Hobson-Imperialism-Yale-ISS-Cain.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.yale.edu/iss/Hobson-Imperialism-Yale-ISS-Cain.pdf" rel="nofollow">J.A. Hobson's Imperialism: A Study: A Centennial Retrospective by Professor Peter Cain</a></li>
